channel.title: New to Delta and to coding
channel.description:
In Delta, where to change:
starter pack logout timer (how long you can stay logged in) starter location (when you create acc) how often d claw spec hits
Im used to PI's but the logout timer and starter location aren't where iwould find em normally, never thought about starter pack too.

item.title: New to Delta and to coding
item.dc:creator: @halflive9 halflive9
item.description:
@halflive9 wrote:

starter pack and starter location:
client.java> search for starter = 0;
Then there will be something like this:

The first 1 is the itemId, the second 1 is the amount.

For the location there will be something like.
X = ####
Y = ####

change the # to your location.

for the logout timer:
client.java> search for TimeOutCounter.
There will be something like:

Make the 20 higher or lower.
